prostate.hex <- h2o.importFile(path= "https://raw.github.com/0xdata/h2o/master/smalldata/logreg/prostate.csv")
data.split <- h2o.splitFrame(data = prostate.hex, ratios = 0.8)
prostate.train <- data.split[[1]]
prostate.test <- data.split[[2]]
prostate.glm <- h2o.glm(y = "CAPSULE", x = c("AGE","RACE","PSA","DCAPS"), training_frame = prostate.train, validation_frame = prostate.test,family = "binomial", nfolds = 10, alpha = 0.5)
prostate.fit <- h2o.predict(object = prostate.glm, newdata = prostate.hex)
summary(prostate.fit)
